@MarcoFalke 
> It looks like you are mostly modifying tests. If the goal it to avoid future code churn, why not add a test-only function that constructs a test-only mempool?

I agree, though in my mind `ChainTestingSetup::ChainTestingSetup` _is_ that "test-only function that constructs a test-only mempool", and I'm just making more tests use it!

